        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: left;
        }
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #d4621c;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #5F9DF7;
            color: white;
        }
        .contact p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .login-button {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #5F9DF7;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>INC 25 - Concepts Judge Allocation</h2>
        <p>Dear <%= data.name %>,</p>
        <p>We hope you are doing well.</p>
        <p>You have been assigned the following projects for evaluation in <strong>Concepts '25</strong>. The judging will take place via <strong>Google Meet</strong>, and a team member will share the Meet link on your WhatsApp number a few minutes before your assigned slot.</p>
        <p>For evaluation, please use the <strong>Judge Portal</strong> to enter the marks directly. However, if you face any difficulties using the portal, kindly fill in the evaluation marksheet attached and upload it to the following Drive link:</p>

        <p><strong>ðŸ”— Drive Link:</strong> <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1MbBbN5Lvs5iLDVYbZiO0ltGWQQ2yopbS?usp=drive_link">Upload Evaluation Marksheet</a></p>
        <p><strong>ðŸ“„ Evaluation Marksheet:</strong> <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1h0umaWn1ylE4hdgDmjjqC8K1O0da7ukdk2NEL1jFvuU/edit?usp=sharing">View Marksheet</a></p>

        <div class="info-box">
            <p><strong>Event:</strong> Concepts</p>
            <p><strong>Judge ID:</strong> <%= data.judge_id %></p>
            <p><strong>Date & Time Slots:</strong> <span style="color: #d4621c;"><strong><%= data.slots %></strong></span></p>
            <p><strong>Mode:</strong> Online (Google Meet)</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote</p>
        </div>

        <h3 style="color: #d4621c;">Allocated Projects</h3>
        <table>
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>PID</th>
                    <th>Title</th>
                    <th>Domain</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% data.projects.forEach(function(project) { %>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= project.pid %></td>
                    <td><%= project.title %></td>
                    <td><%= project.domain %></td>
                    <td><%= project.project_type %></td>
                </tr>
                <% }); %>
            </tbody>
        </table>

        <h3 style="color: #d4621c;">Login Credentials</h3>
        <p>Please login to access detailed information about your allocated projects and evaluation.</p>
        <p><strong>Username:</strong> <%= data.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= data.password %></p>

        <!-- Login Button -->
        <a href="https://pictinc.org/admin" class="login-button">Login to Judge Portal</a>

        <p>If you have any questions or require any assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out. We truly appreciate your time and effort in this process.</p>

